{
  "stem": "8527.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I have the documents from Poland, the court documents that we were finally able to get out after-- after 50 years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there's testimony that I gave and my sister gave in court.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] They came to us and the-- the family said that they would kill us if we would testify against him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1945, right after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I made a statement in here indicating that he helped me and he gave me food when I was in hiding, which was a total lie.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister said basically the same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I heard subsequently through a visit that my sister made to Israel that this man was killed, this Dzujemblo was killed by a Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know what he did?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He found her in a barn and he tied her to a wagon and he tied the other man to a wagon, and he called his neighbors.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they called the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the police didn't come fast enough for him, so he dragged them to-- to town in the wagon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother had a ring, a wedding ring, and he couldn't get it off, so he chopped her finger off.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you can imagine the-- the agony she went through before she died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was marched to the cemetery-- this was in the court records-- and she was-- they laid them down on the floor and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she survived to almost four months before liberation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My dad, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think he wound up in Treblinka, OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And in 1945, the Germans started losing the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Russians were advancing closer to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
